Obtaining the sites with a KLF4 motif

# get KLF4 motif
motif_KLF4 <- query(MotifDb, c("KLF4","Mus"))[[1]]
motif2_KLF4 <- convert_motifs(motif_KLF4, class="TFBSTools-PFMatrix")
## Note: motif [motif] has an empty nsites slot, using 100.
## 
# find motif occurences
# findMotifInstances:
findMotifInstances <- function(seqs, motif, keepMatchedSeq=FALSE, ...){
  motif <- universalmotif::convert_motifs(motif, "TFBSTools-PWMatrix")
  x <- suppressWarnings(TFBSTools::searchSeq(motif, subject=seqs))
  peaks <- strsplit(gsub("-",":",names(seqs)), ":")
  if(!is.null(names(seqs)) && all(lengths(peaks)==3)){ # convert relative coordinates to absolute
    chrs <- sapply(peaks,FUN=function(x) x[1])
    offsets <- sapply(peaks,FUN=function(x) as.integer(x[2]))-1L
    i <- rep(seq_along(x),lengths(x))
    return(GRanges(chrs[i], 
                   IRanges(offsets[i]+as.integer(unlist(lapply(x, start))),
                           offsets[i]+as.integer(unlist(lapply(x, end)))),
                   strand=unlist(lapply(x, strand)),
                   score=as.numeric(unlist(lapply(x, FUN=function(x) score(x))))
                   ))
  }
  x <- as(x, "GRanges")
  score(x) <- x$absScore
  keepFields <- c("score","relScore")
  if(keepMatchedSeq) keepFields <- c(keepFields, "siteSeqs")
  mcols(x) <- mcols(x)[,intersect(colnames(mcols(x)), keepFields)]
  x
}
moi_KLF4 <- findMotifInstances(seqs=chr19, motif=motif2_KLF4,out="positions", p.cutoff=1e-5)

Obtaining the sites with a MAZ motif

# get MAZ motif
motif_MAZ <- query(MotifDb, c("MAZ","Mus"))[[1]]
motif2_MAZ <- convert_motifs(motif_MAZ, class="TFBSTools-PFMatrix")
## Note: motif [motif] has an empty nsites slot, using 100.
# find motif occurences
moi_MAZ <-findMotifInstances(seqs=chr19, motif=motif2_MAZ,out="positions", p.cutoff=1e-5)

Plotting signal around the motif occurences

# we prepare the list of tracks
tracks <- c("Full coverage"="full_cov.bw", "NF coverage"="NF_cov.bw", "All cuts"="full_cuts.bw",
            "NF cuts"="NF_cuts.bw", "Mono cov"="mono_cov.bw", "Mono centers"="mono_centers.bw")

# extract signals around the motif occurences (we zoom in to 500bp around the motif centers, in windows of 5bp)
# KLF4
sm_KLF4 <- signal2Matrix(tracks, moi_KLF4, w=5, extend=500)
## Reading full_cov.bw
## Reading NF_cov.bw
## Reading full_cuts.bw
## Reading NF_cuts.bw
## Reading mono_cov.bw

# MAZ

## Reading full_cov.bw
## Reading NF_cov.bw
## Reading full_cuts.bw
## Reading NF_cuts.bw
## Reading mono_cov.bw

# KLF4

# MAZ

# MAZ
